Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.54,0:00:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（时空幻境之永恒传奇  2）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.84,0:00:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去曾发生战乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.64,0:00:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战后被称为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.95,0:00:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“极光战争”的这场战乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.52,0:00:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是发生在赛雷斯提亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.05,0:00:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和茵费利亚之间的战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.22,0:00:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争结束之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.42,0:00:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茵费利亚和赛雷斯提亚便断绝交流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.12,0:00:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直到今天…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.66,0:00:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.76,0:00:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个世界面临即将灭亡的命运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.90,0:00:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺身而出来拯救这场危机的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.37,0:00:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却是一群无名的年轻人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.94,0:02:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要来妨碍我们！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.64,0:02:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.98,0:02:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.59,0:02:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.99,0:02:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第4话  女人们的大决战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.62,0:02:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.69,0:03:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.69,0:03:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服哦  天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.80,0:03:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮没来对不对？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.20,0:03:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我觉得不太可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.43,0:03:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过她真的躲起来了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.00,0:03:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找她有什么事啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.40,0:03:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想跟她借巴鲁沙渡海到大陆去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.24,0:03:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为台风带来的灾害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.21,0:03:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把镇上的船全弄坏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.01,0:03:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又没必要那么急着离开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.01,0:03:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须尽快到法罗斯山才行呐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.42,0:03:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那个闲工夫再待在这种地方耗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.49,0:03:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有看到玛萝妮就通知我一声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.02,0:03:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.86,0:03:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.16,0:03:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服哦   天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.70,0:03:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛萝妮你在哪里  玛萝妮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.21,0:03:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服哦   天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.32,0:04:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔~暗藏漩涡的可怕大海哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.75,0:04:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴风雨的话是那么的黑暗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.82,0:04:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是天气晴朗的时候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.22,0:04:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可莉娜你在做什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.59,0:04:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  里德大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.93,0:04:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  你跑来这种地方干嘛啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.23,0:04:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那一天的台风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.50,0:04:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺激了我许多的创作灵感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.34,0:04:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我创作了一首接一首的诗歌呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.54,0:04:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~好可怕的台风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.61,0:04:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.08,0:04:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摧毁了不少东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.95,0:04:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.14,0:04:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服哦   天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.61,0:05:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？这啥东东啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.01,0:05:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到玛萝妮了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.62,0:05:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不借！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.52,0:05:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说我会付钱给你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.86,0:05:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没任何理由  我就是不想借
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.36,0:05:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是跟你不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.36,0:05:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那个闲工夫在这里悠哉下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.76,0:05:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是负有拯救世界的使命耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.10,0:06:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭你们？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.70,0:06:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.10,0:06:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意思是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.50,0:06:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭你们的力量是办不到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.71,0:06:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会嘴巴说说的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.74,0:06:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不试试看怎么会知道？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.57,0:06:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个不要再吵了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.41,0:06:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就没有试的必要！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.74,0:06:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔你来一下  基尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.81,0:06:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能说凭你们是办不到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.38,0:06:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就让你瞧瞧我真正的实力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.72,0:06:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看也是不值得看得力量吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.26,0:06:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞燕连脚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.57,0:06:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌底破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.24,0:06:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  快帮我关起来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.81,0:06:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普拉提亚小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.58,0:06:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  是法拉小姐你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.62,0:06:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为发生了什么大事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.75,0:06:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉和玛萝妮你们就别再吵了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.62,0:06:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是没那么容易摆平了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.23,0:07:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是那样的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.96,0:07:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.10,0:07:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就用我们贝鲁卡纽这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.10,0:07:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流传许久的传统方法来做了断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.67,0:07:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位觉得怎么样呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.90,0:07:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传统方法？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.07,0:07:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是“海上试胆”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.61,0:07:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是什么都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.65,0:07:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好极了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.82,0:07:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉…好舒服…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.79,0:07:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.43,0:07:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要举行海上试胆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.73,0:07:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是海上试胆耶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.20,0:07:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.60,0:07:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要举行海上试胆了呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.45,0:07:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们贝鲁卡纽这里…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.81,0:07:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一共有九个小岛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.88,0:07:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在这些小岛之间游泳一圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.75,0:07:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是“海上试胆”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.25,0:08:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自古以来女人之间一旦发生争吵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.62,0:08:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被用来当作解决的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.86,0:08:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且一直沿用至今
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.86,0:08:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算你倒霉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.13,0:08:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是游泳高手中的高手呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.40,0:08:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可真不巧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.77,0:08:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我故乡的拉修安河里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.23,0:08:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也做过不少训练呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.14,0:08:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有烟火了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.54,0:08:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么居民们这么兴奋呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.61,0:08:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为“海上试胆”这个活动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.81,0:08:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是女性都可以自由参加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.38,0:08:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不是一对一单挑啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.38,0:08:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.05,0:08:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要是法拉和玛萝妮以外的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.85,0:08:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先抵达终点的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.42,0:08:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那该怎么办呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.69,0:08:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就判定他们两个人都输
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.69,0:08:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就是实现优胜者的愿望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.29,0:08:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有这样啊~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.69,0:08:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心  我们贝鲁卡纽的女性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.63,0:08:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几乎没什么机会到海里去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.80,0:08:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们只是想穿泳装去玩水而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.57,0:08:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以除了你们两人以外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.84,0:08:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是不会有人真心想游泳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.05,0:08:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这有点太夸张了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.15,0:09:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.78,0:09:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  法拉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.86,0:09:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.73,0:09:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳装  泳装
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.47,0:09:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要买套新泳装
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.00,0:09:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参加“海上试胆”呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.97,0:09:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳装  泳装
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.84,0:09:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海上试胆…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.98,0:09:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海上试胆的历史记录是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.85,0:09:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝鲁卡岛的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.28,0:09:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这泳装是我男朋友买的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.42,0:09:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱哦~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.25,0:09:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了抢夺男人而起争执
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.35,0:09:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是便举行了海上试胆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.82,0:09:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由当时的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.26,0:09:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见证人来作判决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.42,0:09:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且以前领主…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.19,0:09:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正这些都跟我无关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.43,0:09:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去找个安静的地方看天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.10,0:09:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  里德！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.14,0:09:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔  好看吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.81,0:09:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂穿泳装好看吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.21,0:10:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快说啦  基尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.88,0:10:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳装不是我研究的范围内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.01,0:10:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海上试胆  海上试胆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.55,0:10:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~海上试胆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.05,0:10:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有预感将创作出一首很棒的诗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.96,0:10:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海上试胆  海上试…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.12,0:10:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有参加海上试胆哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.29,0:10:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟蜜妮玛买了这套新泳装
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.60,0:10:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得穿起来会不会感觉怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.33,0:10:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看怎么样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.58,0:10:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论谁赢都毫无怨言哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.31,0:10:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得出来你还有一点战士的精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.42,0:10:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,询问我伟大的海洋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.22,0:10:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉·奥尔斯达特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.76,0:10:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和玛萝妮·布鲁卡诺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.73,0:10:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底哪一方才是正确的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.73,0:10:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或这双方都不正确
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.26,0:10:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用您伟大的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.93,0:10:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让正确之人游的更快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.87,0:11:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并引导他回到我们身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.70,0:11:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是泳装吗  基尔？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.51,0:11:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下水游泳不就全掉下来了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.61,0:11:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.34,0:11:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.31,0:11:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是故意要让他掉下来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.18,0:11:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海啊~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.33,0:11:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  相信自己是正确的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.17,0:11:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就游完贝鲁卡纽一周
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.57,0:11:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并拿走这块布吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.67,0:11:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也…也就是说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.91,0:11:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由岛上身份最高的女性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.18,0:11:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是由其代理人来当见证
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.98,0:11:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  我们也下去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.98,0:11:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪花不断溅起的海上试胆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.25,0:12:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到梅露蒂那么会游泳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.08,0:12:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂  右边啦！右边！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.12,0:12:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.26,0:12:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海上试胆好好玩哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.73,0:12:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然只有我跟你一对一单挑呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.83,0:12:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  最后将会是我独霸天下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.73,0:12:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真敢说呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.17,0:12:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是敢说  怎样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.16,0:13:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样而已吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.53,0:13:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然只是嘴巴说说的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.20,0:13:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离终点还久的很呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.07,0:13:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很快就会反败为胜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.47,0:13:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  你那张嘴果然厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.10,0:13:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就会证明给你看的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.94,0:13:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是只有嘴巴…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.27,0:13:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴巴说说的女人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.68,0:13:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌底破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.19,0:13:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞燕连脚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.70,0:13:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为在水中所以威力就减弱了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.07,0:13:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这样的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.94,0:13:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双撞掌底破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.58,0:14:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧  嘴巴说说的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.96,0:14:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好大的胆子竟敢惹我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.13,0:14:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双撞掌底破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.23,0:14:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.26,0:14:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有能站稳脚步的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.80,0:14:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不会有效果的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.57,0:14:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时候要是有剑的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.56,0:14:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要那么乱来呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.63,0:14:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连你都差一点被干掉耶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.33,0:14:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来它受伤了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.67,0:14:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是台风那一天伤到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.83,0:14:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来我是把它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.34,0:14:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏在这附近的无人岛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.34,0:14:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果它察觉到我们有危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.41,0:15:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就拼命飞来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.74,0:15:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.18,0:15:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之所以说不借我们就是因为…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.71,0:15:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说是飞到大陆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.21,0:15:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连像这样稍微飞了一小段路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.18,0:15:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就已经让它够痛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.45,0:15:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要把它藏起来呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.69,0:15:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带它去看医生的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.69,0:15:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会比较快恢复啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.06,0:15:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候为了报恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.72,0:15:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就得载你们到大陆去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.53,0:15:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你打得如意算盘是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.66,0:15:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要把人贬的这么低！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.69,0:15:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.40,0:15:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是担心巴鲁沙的伤势而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.03,0:15:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴鲁沙的主人是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.17,0:15:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么做是我的自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.73,0:15:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.14,0:15:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是就算巴鲁沙怎么样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.91,0:15:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也无所谓吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.57,0:15:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的那么认为吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.01,0:15:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不容许让你这种人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.54,0:15:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来当飞龙的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.98,0:15:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定…要带巴鲁沙去看医生！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.21,0:15:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必你鸡婆！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.23,0:15:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准你动巴鲁沙一根汗毛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.13,0:15:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卧龙空破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.77,0:16:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就只会口是心非而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.34,0:16:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双撞掌底破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.61,0:16:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实你真的很担心巴鲁沙嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.51,0:16:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三散华
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.08,0:16:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是失去了巴鲁沙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.38,0:16:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连牙弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.81,0:16:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就没有可以移动的工具了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.72,0:16:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞燕连脚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.92,0:16:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这人还真不坦率
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.75,0:16:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞燕连脚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.85,0:16:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  你没那资格说我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.92,0:16:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连牙弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.96,0:16:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我赢了这次的海上试胆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.93,0:16:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就要请求治好巴鲁沙的伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.40,0:16:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.00,0:16:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先说的啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.30,0:16:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先说的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.84,0:16:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我啦  是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.21,0:16:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.21,0:16:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.07,0:16:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散华猛袭脚  双撞掌底破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.18,0:16:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.25,0:16:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然我们的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.69,0:16:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是治好巴鲁沙的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.49,0:16:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就没必要再比下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.40,0:17:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这地方就安全了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.30,0:17:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会马上带医生来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.77,0:17:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要乖乖的在这里等哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.78,0:17:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  巴鲁沙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.41,0:17:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痒哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.57,0:17:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.04,0:17:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打从刚才就吱吱的叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.91,0:17:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.58,0:17:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我唯一的愿望…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.05,0:17:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想安安静静的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.18,0:17:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仰望天空而已！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.15,0:18:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔神连牙斩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.77,0:18:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来来来  又冰又凉的饮料哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.74,0:18:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有很好喝很好喝的冰饮料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.41,0:18:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有人要买啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.11,0:18:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉他们怎么动作那么慢哪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.01,0:18:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照理说应该差不多要回来了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.15,0:18:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就…就是说啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.85,0:18:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是发生了什么事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.95,0:18:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是他们两人的话  那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.60,0:18:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅…梅露蒂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.53,0:18:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海上试胆  是梅露蒂获胜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.07,0:18:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可喜可贺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.47,0:18:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~可喜可贺  可喜可贺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.14,0:18:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海上试胆~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.15,0:19:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梅露蒂赢了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.52,0:19:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来医疗费得自费了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.18,0:19:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起参赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.25,0:19:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.69,0:19:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要参赛…  不必…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.52,0:19:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优胜者请到这里来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.66,0:19:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.99,0:19:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要出…  不必…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.53,0:19:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海已经判定你是正确的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.80,0:19:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  请说出你的愿望吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.84,0:19:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉  玛萝妮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.57,0:19:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要出…  不必…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.41,0:19:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉  玛萝妮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.31,0:19:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露蒂的愿望是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.15,0:19:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望法拉  玛萝妮你们能够和好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.32,0:19:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.89,0:19:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我答应你会跟她和好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.43,0:19:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此产生了一份新的情谊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.03,0:19:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是里德他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.57,0:19:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还困在贝鲁卡纽的情形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.27,0:19:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却仍旧没有改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.41,0:20:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有虫子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.84,0:20:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也看不到人类和怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.68,0:20:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.98,0:20:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算可以安安静静的眺望天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.59,0:20:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.93,0:20:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请期待下回精彩好戏


